name: grocery
0:
”Alexa, ask grocery manager to get my grocery list”
”Alexa, ask grocery manager to add onion 1 lb”
”Alexa, ask grocery manager to clear my grocery list”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: grocery manager
des:
This skill enables you to manage your grocery list or any kind of list.
To add items : "add name_of_grocery"
To clear items : "clear"
To list items : "list"
To send email: "send email to <<your email>>"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
